    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate gravity, walk on walls, and uncover secrets in this atmospheric dungeon puzzler where every room offers a completely unique idea.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAWL ON THE WALLS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flex your spatial reasoning skills as you walk on the walls in order to delve deeper into the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/cd3b5946baa684d54f2fe845394633c2.poster.avif?t=1748542181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/cd3b5946baa684d54f2fe845394633c2.webm?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/cd3b5946baa684d54f2fe845394633c2.mp4?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIRE YOUR ARROW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your bow is the primary tool at your disposal, however you've got just one arrow. Recall the arrow from anywhere to retrieve it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/fe43205ad460ceead2492a1d450efb1c.poster.avif?t=1748542181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/fe43205ad460ceead2492a1d450efb1c.webm?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/fe43205ad460ceead2492a1d450efb1c.mp4?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO FILLER CONTENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each puzzle offers a completely unique idea, carefully designed to surprise and delight you as the core set of mechanics goes deeper and deeper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/f9393d14f9fdba091d2d6b16982b1870.poster.avif?t=1748542181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/f9393d14f9fdba091d2d6b16982b1870.webm?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381760/extras/f9393d14f9fdba091d2d6b16982b1870.mp4?t=1748542181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
